    "LLM_NLP": "Autoregressive LLMs minimize token-level loss in ways that overfit attention heads to prompt-template artifacts, so decoding steps rely on spurious lexical tokens rather than task semantics; performance degrades when in-context examples or formatting are perturbed, exposing shortcut dependence.",
